{"tid":2436657,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國禁內蒙古挖加密貨幣   控制環境污染問題","createTime":"2021-03-07T10:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T12:05:45.000Z","uid":310867,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e02509a4decd6d697078890eb84fcd1e26eeff4","tid":2436657,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"由於內蒙古電價低廉，嚴重污染環境。有見及此，內蒙古自治區日前發改委發布了《關於確保完成 &rdquo;十四五&rdquo; 能耗雙控目標任務若干保障措施（徵求意見稿）》文件，宣布禁止開採加密貨幣，並希望在今年 4 月前關閉所有加密貨幣採礦場。<br />\n<br />\n近年中國一直積極推動減少碳排放量及能源消耗的目標，為確保能源消耗得到有效的控管，中國政府計畫在 4 月底以前關閉內蒙古內的虛擬貨幣礦場，並禁止新虛擬貨幣挖礦場在內蒙古進行投資建廠。<br />\n<br />\n現宣布禁止採礦，可能會動搖中國在虛擬貨幣挖礦業的地位。措施宣布後，比特幣的價格上漲了 3％。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/03/07/nmg-bitcoin-banned/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR3AqQcr6b84Ionj_yfOci0S7YyrwqOCoyNg9D0jfeLzf6AbFB5G86Gx5OQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F03%2F07%2Fnmg-bitcoin-banned%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3AqQcr6b84Ionj_yfOci0S7YyrwqOCoyNg9D0jfeLzf6AbFB5G86Gx5OQ&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=ae327271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/03/07/nmg-bitcoin-banned/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR3AqQcr6b84Ionj_yfOci0S7YyrwqOCoyNg9D0jfeLzf6AbFB5G86Gx5OQ</a>"},{"pid":"98d069873a22da40256c2a57d358018f4123ba96","tid":2436657,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"官方開發"},{"pid":"9ac2c3161834a4934dc39878d15ce96419129f59","tid":2436657,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"唔係用再生能源架咩"},{"pid":"367d2a0ea023d1ca6f17cdbdd5af33b00393b78d","tid":2436657,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmjHudn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmjHudn.png&h=151d9ac4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8b4f9684d4e8361c8f04e08c0d4ae40dcd5998d","tid":2436657,"uid":74778,"like":11,"di